&lt;h3 id="_ingredients"&gt;Ingredients&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="sectionbody"&gt;
&lt;table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all stretch"&gt;
&lt;colgroup&gt;
&lt;col style="width: 50%;"&gt;
&lt;col style="width: 50%;"&gt;
&lt;/colgroup&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"&gt;&lt;p class="tableblock"&gt;1/4 cup flour&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"&gt;&lt;p class="tableblock"&gt;1/2 teaspoon salt&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"&gt;&lt;p class="tableblock"&gt;1/4 teaspoon pepper&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"&gt;&lt;p class="tableblock"&gt;1/2 teaspoon oregano&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"&gt;&lt;p class="tableblock"&gt;4 tablespoons butter&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"&gt;&lt;p class="tableblock"&gt;1 cup sliced mushrooms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"&gt;&lt;p class="tableblock"&gt;1 1/2 cup marsala wine&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"&gt;&lt;p class="tableblock"&gt;3/4 cup cooking sherry&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="sect1"&gt;
&lt;h3 id="_directions"&gt;Directions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="sectionbody"&gt;
&lt;div class="olist arabic"&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In a small bowl, combine flour, salt, pepper, and oregano. Coat chicken pieces in mixture and set aside.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In large skillet, melt butter in oil over medium heat. Cook chicken until lightly brown.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add mushrooms, sherry, and marsala.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cover skillet and simmer until checken is fully cooked.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thicken sauce with water/cornstarch&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
